fields.name: OpenStreetMap Tiles
fields.config:
layers:
 - name: imagery
   title: imagery
   sources: [cache]

sources:
  imagery_wmts:
    type: tile
    grid: webmercator
    url: http://a.tile.openstreetmap.fr/hot/%(z)s/%(x)s/%(y)s.png

grids:
  webmercator:
    srs: EPSG:3857
    tile_size: [256, 256]
    origin: nw

fields.name: ESRI-Imagery
fields.config:
layer:
  - name: imagery
    title: imagery
    sources: [cache]

sources:
  imagery_arcgis:
    type: arcgis
    grid: webmercator
    req:
      url: http://server.arcgisonline.com/arcgis/rest/services/ESRI_Imagery_World_2D/MapServer
      layers: 
        show: 0

grids:
  webmercator:
    srs: EPSG:3857
    tile_size: [256, 256]
    origin: nw
